s aspirations\", \"from\": 253, \"to\": 268}, {\"ngram\": \"further glory\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"the international stage\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arshad Nadeem, who made history with his gold medal win at the Paris 2024 Olympics, expressed his determination to defend his title at the 2028 Olympics and, health permitting, to participate in the 2032 Games as well.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arshad Nadeem\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"his gold medal win\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 388}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"his determination\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"his title\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2028 Olympics\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"health permitting\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2032 Games\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 542}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stated, This is just the beginning of my journey.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just the beginning\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to defend my title in 2028, and if I stay fit, I intend to participate in the 2032 Olympics as well.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my title\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 631}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2032 Olympics\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reflecting on the overwhelming support he has received, Arshad recounted the warm reception at Lahore Airport, where he was honored by the Chief Minister and the Prime Minister, who invited him to the PM House on Independence Day.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the overwhelming support\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 7